```plantuml
@startuml Sanperolo_The-Intelligent-Bike

participant "Bike Sensors" as Sensors
participant "Hardware Interface" as Hardware
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "Backend API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Frontend Dashboard" as Frontend

Sensors -> Hardware: Collect sensor data
Hardware -> Hardware: Process data
Hardware -> MQTT: Publish sensor data
MQTT -> API: Forward sensor data
API -> DB: Store sensor data
Frontend -> API: Request sensor data
API -> DB: Query sensor data
DB --> API: Return sensor data
API --> Frontend: Send sensor data
Frontend -> Frontend: Display data

@enduml
```